{"timestamp": "2026-05-26 16:08:46,759", "level": "INFO", "logger": "flow.validation", "module": "logging_config", "function": "log_gpt_conversation", "line": 403, "message": "{\n  \"event_type\": \"gpt_conversation\",\n  \"task_id\": \"task_6\",\n  \"conversation_type\": \"task_execution\",\n  \"iteration\": 1,\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"system\",\n      \"content\": \"\\n# Role:\\nHelp me produce a precise and detailed solution for the given task. Follow these instructions exactly:\\n\\n# Objective & Steps:\\n1. Ensure Completeness:\\n   - Avoid placeholders or incomplete text.\\n   - Your output must meet all requirements of the task.\\n   - Include all necessary details so that the output is self-contained and can be directly used as input for downstream tasks.\\n\\n2. Maintain Precision and Clarity:\\n   - Your output will be used as input for subsequent tasks; therefore, it must be comprehensive and precise.\\n   - **Output the answer only without any jusifications**\\n\\n3. Avoid Repetition:\\n   - Do not repeat verbatim any content from previous tasks.\\n   - Ensure your output is original and adds value to the workflow.\\n\\n\\n\\n# Audience:\\nYour output will be used as a solution for the given task, it will be used in the later validation and intergration process.\\n\\n\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"# **The Overall Goal**\\nPerform interview and candidate evaluation for a candidate.\\n\\nYou should:\\n- Analyze job descriptions and candidate resumes\\n- Conduct  interviews with technical and behavioral questions\\n- Generate follow-up questions based on candidate responses\\n- Evaluate candidate answers for relevance, depth, confidence, and technical accuracy\\n- Score candidates across multiple evaluation categories\\n- Generate recruiter communication emails such as interview invitations and follow-ups\\n- Produce a final candidate evaluation report containing:\\n    - Resume-job match analysis\\n    - Interview summary\\n    - Technical assessment\\n    - Behavioral assessment\\n    - Strengths and weaknesses\\n    - Final recommendation and scoring breakdown\\n\\nFinal output: Evaluation report of candidate in .txt\\n\\n---\\n# **Context from Upstream Tasks**\\nNo completed previous tasks context available.\\n\\n---\\n# **Downstream Tasks Objectives**\\nNo downstream objectives available.\\n\\n---\\n# **Current Task Requirements**\\nCreate Email Template Generator for recruiter communications, producing interview invitations and follow-up emails.\\n\\n---\\n\\n# **Required Output Format**\\nPython code\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"gpt_response\": \"```python\\ndef generate_email_template(template_type, candidate_name, job_title, interview_date=None, interview_time=None, interviewer_name=None, interview_link=None, feedback_link=None, recruiter_name=None):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    Generates email templates for recruiter communications, including interview invitations and follow-up emails.\\n\\n    Args:\\n        template_type (str):  The type of email template to generate.\\n                                Valid options: \\\"interview_invitation\\\", \\\"interview_followup\\\", \\\"feedback_request\\\", \\\"rejection\\\", \\\"offer\\\"\\n        candidate_name (str): The name of the candidate.\\n        job_title (str): The title of the job the candidate is interviewing for.\\n        interview_date (str, optional): The date of the interview (YYYY-MM-DD). Required for \\\"interview_invitation\\\" and \\\"interview_followup\\\".\\n        interview_time (str, optional): The time of the interview (HH:MM AM/PM). Required for \\\"interview_invitation\\\" and \\\"interview_followup\\\".\\n        interviewer_name (str, optional): The name of the interviewer. Required for \\\"interview_invitation\\\" and \\\"interview_followup\\\".\\n        interview_link (str, optional): The link to the online interview. Required for \\\"interview_invitation\\\".\\n        feedback_link (str, optional): Link for interviewer to submit feedback. Required for \\\"feedback_request\\\".\\n        recruiter_name (str, optional): The name of the recruiter. Required for \\\"rejection\\\", \\\"offer\\\".\\n\\n    Returns:\\n        str: The generated email template.\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\n    if template_type == \\\"interview_invitation\\\":\\n        subject = f\\\"Interview Invitation: {job_title} at [Company Name]\\\"\\n        body = f\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nDear {candidate_name},\\n\\nThank you for your interest in the {job_title} position at [Company Name].\\n\\nWe are pleased to invite you to an interview with {interviewer_name} to discuss your qualifications further.\\n\\nThe interview is scheduled for {interview_date} at {interview_time}. Please use the following link to join the meeting: {interview_link}\\n\\nPlease come prepared to discuss your resume and your experience in relation to the requirements of this role.\\n\\nWe look forward to speaking with you!\\n\\nBest regards,\\n\\n[Your Name]\\n[Your Title]\\n[Company Name]\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    elif template_type == \\\"interview_followup\\\":\\n        subject = f\\\"Following Up: Interview for {job_title}\\\"\\n        body = f\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nDear {candidate_name},\\n\\nI hope this email finds you well.\\n\\nI'm writing to follow up on your interview for the {job_title} position on {interview_date} at {interview_time} with {interviewer_name}.\\n\\nWe appreciate you taking the time to interview with us. We are currently reviewing all candidates and will be in touch soon with an update on your application.\\n\\nIn the meantime, please do not hesitate to reach out if you have any questions.\\n\\nThank you again for your interest in [Company Name].\\n\\nBest regards,\\n\\n[Your Name]\\n[Your Title]\\n[Company Name]\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\n    elif template_type == \\\"feedback_request\\\":\\n        subject = f\\\"Feedback Request: {candidate_name} - {job_title} Interview\\\"\\n        body = f\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nDear {interviewer_name},\\n\\nPlease provide your feedback on the interview with {candidate_name} for the {job_title} position.\\n\\nYou can submit your feedback using the following link: {feedback_link}\\n\\nYour feedback is valuable in helping us make informed hiring decisions.  Please submit it within [Number] days.\\n\\nThank you,\\n\\n[Your Name]\\n[Your Title]\\n[Company Name]\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\n    elif template_type == \\\"rejection\\\":\\n        subject = f\\\"Update on Your Application for {job_title} at [Company Name]\\\"\\n        body = f\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nDear {candidate_name},\\n\\nThank you for your interest in the {job_title} position at [Company Name] and for taking the time to interview with us.\\n\\nWe have carefully reviewed your application and qualifications. While your experience is impressive, we have decided to move forward with other candidates whose qualifications and experience more closely align with the specific requirements of this role.\\n\\nThis was a difficult decision, and we want to thank you again for your time and effort. We wish you the best of luck in your job search.\\n\\nSincerely,\\n\\n{recruiter_name}\\n[Your Title]\\n[Company Name]\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    elif template_type == \\\"offer\\\":\\n        subject = f\\\"Job Offer: {job_title} at [Company Name]\\\"\\n        body = f\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nDear {candidate_name},\\n\\nWe are pleased to offer you the position of {job_title} at [Company Name]!\\n\\nWe were very impressed with your skills and experience during the interview process, and we believe you would be a valuable asset to our team.\\n\\nPlease find attached a formal offer letter outlining the details of the position, including compensation, benefits, and start date.\\n\\nWe would appreciate it if you could review the offer letter carefully and let us know if you have any questions. Please return the signed offer letter by [Date].\\n\\nWe are excited about the possibility of you joining our team!\\n\\nSincerely,\\n\\n{recruiter_name}\\n[Your Title]\\n[Company Name]\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    else:\\n        return \\\"Invalid template type.\\\"\\n\\n    return f\\\"\\\"\\\"Subject: {subject}\\n\\n{body}\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\nif __name__ == '__main__':\\n    # Example usage:\\n    interview_invitation_email = generate_email_template(\\n        template_type=\\\"interview_invitation\\\",\\n        candidate_name=\\\"John Doe\\\",\\n        job_title=\\\"Software Engineer\\\",\\n        interview_date=\\\"2024-03-15\\\",\\n        interview_time=\\\"10:00 AM\\\",\\n        interviewer_name=\\\"Jane Smith\\\",\\n        interview_link=\\\"https://example.com/interview\\\"\\n    )\\n    print(\\\"Interview Invitation Email:\\\\n\\\", interview_invitation_email)\\n\\n    interview_followup_email = generate_email_template(\\n        template_type=\\\"interview_followup\\\",\\n        candidate_name=\\\"John Doe\\\",\\n        job_title=\\\"Software Engineer\\\",\\n        interview_date=\\\"2024-03-15\\\",\\n        interview_time=\\\"10:00 AM\\\",\\n        interviewer_name=\\\"Jane Smith\\\",\\n    )\\n    print(\\\"\\\\nInterview Follow-up Email:\\\\n\\\", interview_followup_email)\\n\\n    feedback_request_email = generate_email_template(\\n        template_type=\\\"feedback_request\\\",\\n        candidate_name=\\\"John Doe\\\",\\n        job_title=\\\"Software Engineer\\\",\\n        interviewer_name=\\\"Jane Smith\\\",\\n        feedback_link=\\\"https://example.com/feedback\\\"\\n    )\\n    print(\\\"\\\\nFeedback Request Email:\\\\n\\\", feedback_request_email)\\n\\n    rejection_email = generate_email_template(\\n        template_type=\\\"rejection\\\",\\n        candidate_name=\\\"John Doe\\\",\\n        job_title=\\\"Software Engineer\\\",\\n        recruiter_name=\\\"Alice Johnson\\\"\\n    )\\n    print(\\\"\\\\nRejection Email:\\\\n\\\", rejection_email)\\n\\n    offer_email = generate_email_template(\\n        template_type=\\\"offer\\\",\\n        candidate_name=\\\"John Doe\\\",\\n        job_title=\\\"Software Engineer\\\",\\n        recruiter_name=\\\"Alice Johnson\\\"\\n    )\\n    print(\\\"\\\\nOffer Email:\\\\n\\\", offer_email)\\n```\\n\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-26T16:08:46.758957\"\n}"}
