{"timestamp": "2026-05-26 16:09:07,544", "level": "INFO", "logger": "flow.validation", "module": "logging_config", "function": "log_validation_result", "line": 185, "message": "{\"timestamp\": \"2026-05-26T16:09:07.544659\", \"task_id\": \"unknown\", \"task_objective\": \"Create Email Template Generator for recruiter communications, producing interview invitations and follow-up emails.\", \"result\": \"```python\\ndef generate_email_template(template_type, candidate_name, job_title, interview_date=None, interview_time=None, interviewer_name=None, interview_link=None, feedback_link=None, recruiter_name=None):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    Generates email templates for recruiter communications, including interview invitations and follow-up emails.\\n\\n    Args:\\n        template_type (str):  The type of email template to generate.\\n                                Valid options: \\\"interview_invitation\\\", \\\"interview_followu...\", \"validation_type\": \"text\", \"status\": \"completed\", \"feedback\": \"here are some feedbacks:\\n1. The function currently uses hardcoded placeholders like `[Company Name]`, `[Your Name]`, and `[Your Title]` instead of accepting dynamic parameters.\\n2. The `recruiter_name` parameter is not used in the invitation and follow-up templates.\\n3. There’s no `company_name` parameter to customize the company’s name.\\n4. Required parameters for each template type aren’t validated, which may lead to incomplete emails.\\n5. The indentation in the multi-line string bodies results in extra leading spaces.\\n\\nhere are the changes:\\n```python\\nimport textwrap\\n\\ndef generate_email_template(\\n    template_type,\\n    candidate_name,\\n    job_title,\\n    company_name,\\n    recruiter_name,\\n    interviewer_name=None,\\n    interview_date=None,\\n    interview_time=None,\\n    interview_link=None,\\n    feedback_link=None,\\n    your_title=None\\n):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    Generates email templates for recruiter communications, including:\\n    - interview invitations\\n    - interview follow-ups\\n    - feedback requests\\n    - rejections\\n    - offers\\n\\n    Args:\\n        template_type (str): Type of email. One of:\\n            \\\"interview_invitation\\\", \\\"interview_followup\\\",\\n            \\\"feedback_request\\\", \\\"rejection\\\", \\\"offer\\\"\\n        candidate_name (str): Candidate's full name.\\n        job_title (str): Title of the role.\\n        company_name (str): Name of the company.\\n        recruiter_name (str): Name of the recruiter sending the mail.\\n        interviewer_name (str, optional): Name of the interviewer.\\n            Required for invitations and follow-ups.\\n        interview_date (str, optional): Date of interview (YYYY-MM-DD).\\n            Required for invitations and follow-ups.\\n        interview_time (str, optional): Time of interview (e.g., \\\"10:00 AM\\\").\\n            Required for invitations and follow-ups.\\n        interview_link (str, optional): Link for online interview.\\n            Required for invitations.\\n        feedback_link (str, optional): Link for interviewer feedback.\\n            Required for feedback requests.\\n        your_title (str, optional): Recruiter's title.\\n\\n    Returns:\\n        str: Formatted email with Subject and Body.\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    # Validate required fields per template\\n    if template_type in (\\\"interview_invitation\\\", \\\"interview_followup\\\"):\\n        if not all([interviewer_name, interview_date, interview_time]):\\n            raise ValueError(f\\\"Missing interviewer_name, interview_date, or interview_time for {template_type}\\\")\\n    if template_type == \\\"interview_invitation\\\" and not interview_link:\\n        raise ValueError(\\\"Missing interview_link for interview_invitation\\\")\\n    if template_type == \\\"feedback_request\\\" and not feedback_link:\\n        raise ValueError(\\\"Missing feedback_link for feedback_request\\\")\\n\\n    # Common sign-off\\n    title_line = f\\\"{recruiter_name}\\\"\\n    if your_title:\\n        title_line += f\\\"\\\\n{your_title}\\\"\\n    title_line += f\\\"\\\\n{company_name}\\\"\\n\\n    if template_type == \\\"interview_invitation\\\":\\n        subject = f\\\"Interview Invitation: {job_title} at {company_name}\\\"\\n        body = f\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nDear {candidate_name},\\n\\nThank you for applying to the {job_title} position at {company_name}.\\nWe’re pleased to invite you to an interview with {interviewer_name}.\\n\\nDate: {interview_date}\\nTime: {interview_time}\\nJoin via: {interview_link}\\n\\nPlease review your resume and come prepared to discuss how your skills align with this role.\\n\\nWe look forward to meeting you!\\n\\nBest regards,\\n{title_line}\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    elif template_type == \\\"interview_followup\\\":\\n        subject = f\\\"Follow-Up: {job_title} Interview at {company_name}\\\"\\n        body = f\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nDear {candidate_name},\\n\\nI hope you’re doing well.\\n\\nI’m reaching out regarding your interview for the {job_title} position on {interview_date} at {interview_time} with {interviewer_name}.\\nWe appreciate your time and are reviewing all candidates. We will update you soon on next steps.\\n\\nFeel free to let me know if you have any questions.\\n\\nThank you again for your interest in {company_name}.\\n\\nBest regards,\\n{title_line}\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    elif template_type == \\\"feedback_request\\\":\\n        subject = f\\\"Feedback Request: {candidate_name} – {job_title}\\\"\\n        body = f\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nHi {interviewer_name},\\n\\nCould you please provide your feedback on the interview with {candidate_name} for the {job_title} role?\\nSubmit your feedback here: {feedback_link}\\n\\nYour insights are vital for our hiring decision. Please return your feedback within 3 business days.\\n\\nThank you,\\n{title_line}\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    elif template_type == \\\"rejection\\\":\\n        subject = f\\\"Update on Your Application for {job_title} at {company_name}\\\"\\n        body = f\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nDear {candidate_name},\\n\\nThank you for interviewing with us for the {job_title} role at {company_name}.\\nAfter careful consideration, we’ve decided to move forward with other candidates whose experience more closely matches our requirements.\\n\\nWe appreciate your interest and wish you success in your job search.\\n\\nSincerely,\\n{title_line}\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    elif template_type == \\\"offer\\\":\\n        subject = f\\\"Job Offer: {job_title} at {company_name}\\\"\\n        body = f\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nDear {candidate_name},\\n\\nCongratulations! We are excited to offer you the position of {job_title} at {company_name}.\\nPlease find the formal offer letter attached outlining compensation, benefits, and start date.\\nKindly review and return a signed copy by the specified date.\\n\\nWe look forward to having you on our team!\\n\\nWarm regards,\\n{title_line}\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    else:\\n        raise ValueError(f\\\"Invalid template_type: {template_type}\\\")\\n\\n    # Clean up indentation\\n    email_text = f\\\"Subject: {subject}\\\\n\\\\n{ textwrap.dedent(body).strip() }\\\"\\n    return email_text\\n\\n\\n# Example usage\\nif __name__ == \\\"__main__\\\":\\n    invite = generate_email_template(\\n        template_type=\\\"interview_invitation\\\",\\n        candidate_name=\\\"John Doe\\\",\\n        job_title=\\\"Software Engineer\\\",\\n        company_name=\\\"TechCorp Inc.\\\",\\n        recruiter_name=\\\"Alice Johnson\\\",\\n        your_title=\\\"Recruiting Manager\\\",\\n        interviewer_name=\\\"Jane Smith\\\",\\n        interview_date=\\\"2024-03-15\\\",\\n        interview_time=\\\"10:00 AM\\\",\\n        interview_link=\\\"https://meet.example.com/techcorp\\\"\\n    )\\n    print(invite)\\n    \\n    followup = generate_email_template(\\n        template_type=\\\"interview_followup\\\",\\n        candidate_name=\\\"John Doe\\\",\\n        job_title=\\\"Software Engineer\\\",\\n        company_name=\\\"TechCorp Inc.\\\",\\n        recruiter_name=\\\"Alice Johnson\\\",\\n        your_title=\\\"Recruiting Manager\\\",\\n        interviewer_name=\\\"Jane Smith\\\",\\n        interview_date=\\\"2024-03-15\\\",\\n        interview_time=\\\"10:00 AM\\\"\\n    )\\n    print(\\\"\\\\n\\\" + followup)\\n```\\n\"}"}
